msgstr "Cloudflare Turnstile site key"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:450
msgid ""
"From your Cloudflare Turnstile widget (dash.cloudflare.com → Turnstile). "
"Adds a human-verification check to the public Subscribe (newsletter-signup) "
"and Join forms. Leave either key blank to leave both forms exactly as they "
"are today."
msgstr ""
"From your Cloudflare Turnstile widget (dash.cloudflare.com → Turnstile). "
"Adds a human-verification check to the public Subscribe (newsletter-signup) "
"and Join forms. Leave either key blank to leave both forms exactly as they "
"are today."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:454
msgid "Cloudflare Turnstile secret key"
msgstr "Cloudflare Turnstile secret key"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:457
msgid ""
"Kept server-side only — used to verify each form submission directly with "
